source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_00<tab>789th Order Dustman Bo Zu has a friend in need of a helping hand─preferably not Bo Zu's.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_00<tab>Im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens sorgt sich Bo Zu um einen Gefährten.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_01<tab>Bo Zu considers the 789th Order's acolyte, the eccentric Ba Go, one of his closest friends at the dig─a feeling which does not appear to be in any way mutual. With Ba Go in trouble and seeking the assistance of anyone not named Bo Zu, go and offer what help you may.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_01<tab>Ba Go hat wohl ein Problem, das deine Aufmerksamkeit erfordert. Frage den Kobold-Alchemisten, was los ist.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_02<tab>From what sense you can make of Ba Go's ramblings, a few of his so-called beauties─unhappy with their creator's treatment of them─have flown the coop and now wreak havoc in the vicinity of Iron Lake. At Ba Go's behest, seek them out and /soothe their anger, that they might return home and trouble innocent bystanders no more.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_02<tab>Ba Gos geliebte Mini-Bomber hatten Freigang und sind noch nicht zurückgekehrt. Suche die fünf aufgedrehten Ausreißer am Eisensee und beruhige sie (Emote: Beruhigen; Textbefehl: /ruhig).

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_03<tab>Their volatile hearts calmed, the pygmy bombs have returned to the loving care of their creator. Return to Ba Go in triumph.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_03<tab>Du hast alle Mini-Bomber beruhigt, sodass sie zu ihrem „Vater“ zurückkehren werden. Melde dich bei Ba Go.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_04<tab>Eager to make amends, Ba Go is far too preoccupied doting on his beauties to express any sort of gratitude for your part in securing their safe return. Return to Bo Zu and inform him that the deed is done.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_04<tab>Alle Ausreißer sind zu Ba Go zurückgekehrt, worüber der alte Kobold überaus glücklich ist. Sag Bo Zu Bescheid, dass du das Problem klären konntest.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_05<tab>Bo Zu is deeply appreciative of your efforts on behalf of his friend Ba Go, who he still considers a friend despite the latter's utter disregard for the hapless dustman. Having demonstrated both generosity and competence, you can expect Bo Zu to call upon you again next time he or one of his peers is in need...
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SEQ_05<tab>Bo Zu ist froh, dass du Ba Gos Problem zu seiner Zufriedenheit lösen konntest. Er hofft, dass du ihm und den anderen Kobolden des 789. Ordens ebenso gut helfen wirst.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_TODO_00<tab>Speak with 789th Order Acolyte Ba Go.
TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_TODO_01<tab>/soothe pygmy bombs at Iron Lake.
TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_TODO_02<tab>Speak with 789th Order Acolyte Ba Go.
TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_TODO_03<tab>Report to 789th Order Dustman Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_TODO_03<tab>Bo Zu von der Problemlösung erzählen

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_000<tab>Adventurer, how glad, glad I am to see you come. Ba Go is having a situation─a plight, a predicament, a situation─and what is trouble for Ba Go is trouble for us all. Bo Zu does not know much, but this Bo Zu knows. Yes, yes, I know.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_000<tab>Ohoh, Ba Go Problem hat! Ihm nicht helfen ich kann! Was er macht, viel zu hoch für mich.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_001<tab>Bo Zu would like nothing more than to help his friend Ba Go─nothing, nothing at all. But Bo Zu's help is unwelcome─unsought, undesired, unwelcome. This makes Bo Zu sad, but what can Bo Zu do? Only send you─yes, yes, Bo Zu will send you.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_001<tab>Aber du ihm helfen kannst, ja, ja! Sprich mit ihm, ja, ja!

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_002<tab>Bo Zu would like nothing more than to help his friend Ba Go─nothing, nothing at all. But Bo Zu's help is unwelcome─unsought, undesired, unwelcome. This makes Bo Zu sad, but what can Bo Zu do? Only send you─yes, yes, Bo Zu will send you!
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_002<tab>Ba Go du helfen kannst, ja, ja! Sprich mit ihm, ja, ja!

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_010<tab>Bo Zu sent you to me, he did? You will not eat my beauties' fingers and make my workshop go boom-boom like that one did? No, no, you will not?
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_010<tab>Bo Zu dich schickt? An mich denkt der Gute. Tatsächlich ein Problem ich habe.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_011<tab>Then maybe you can be of assistance─help, aid, assistance. With some of my beauties did I have a disagreement─a spat, a fight, a disagreement. Fled my workshop, they did, fled to Iron Lake where they seethe and sizzle and speak ill of Ba Go.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_011<tab>Meine lieben, kleinen Mini-Bomber noch nicht vom Spielen nach Hause gekommen. Am Eisensee sie sich noch immer herumtreiben.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_012<tab>You will tell them Ba Go is sorry for what he said, yes? They are not getting fat─no, no─they are as slender, slim, and beautiful as ever. They will come back to Ba Go, yes? Ba Go implores of them─begs, beseeches, implores.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_012<tab>Zu mir zurück du sie schickst, ja? Gute Kinder sie sind. Wenn du sie <var 1A 02 /var>beruhigst<var 1A 01 /var>, sie bestimmt auf dich hören.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_013<tab>You will go to Iron Lake and bring runaway beauties back to Ba Go, yes? Tell them Ba Go is sorry for everything he said? Ba Go is nothing without his beauties...<sniff>...no, no, nothing.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_013<tab>Meine lieben Mini-Bomber zu mir zurück du schickst, ja? Gute Kinder sie sind. Wenn du sie <var 1A 02 /var>beruhigst<var 1A 01 /var>, sie bestimmt auf dich hören.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>The pygmy bomb is fuming with rage. <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Soothe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> it and convince it to return home to its master.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>Der Mini-Bomber scheint schlecht gelaunt zu sein und macht keine Anstalten, zu Ba Go zurückzukehren. Du musst den Mini-Bomber erst <var 1A 02 /var>beruhigen<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SYSTEM_000_016<tab>The pygmy bomb is not amused. <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Soothe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> it and convince it to return home to its master.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_SYSTEM_000_016<tab>Jetzt ist der Mini-Bomber noch viel schlechter gelaunt. <var 1A 02 /var>Beruhige<var 1A 01 /var> ihn, damit er zu Ba Go zurückkehrt

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_020<tab>My beauties...my beauties return! Oh, glorious day! Ba Go was lost without you─wayward, astray, lost. Yes, yes, he was!
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_020<tab>Jahaha, alle meine kleinen Mini-Bomber sind wieder zu Hause. Danke, danke!

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_021<tab>Ba Go was a fool─a dolt, a dimwit, a fool! Foolish Ba Go will do anything you desire! Yes, yes, just promise you will never leave Ba Go's side ag─hm? Can't you see we are having a personal moment here, adventurer? Yes, yes, go back and bother Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BAGO_000_021<tab>Wirklich zu gebrauchen du bist! Bo Zu meinen Gruß ausrichte, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_030<tab><sigh> That is Ba Go for you─no eye for anything but booms and beauties. He may not call Bo Zu friend, but does this change Bo Zu's feelings? No, no, never.
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_030<tab>Ba Go du helfen konntest? Bedankt er sich hat? Dann er dich sehr mögen!

source: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_031<tab>I cannot speak for Ba Go─no, no, I cannot─but Bo Zu will not forget your kindness. Yes, Bo Zu will always remember who to ask when he needs something done. Yes, yes, I will!
target: TEXT_BANKOB109_01333_BOZU_000_031<tab>Ich dich auch mögen! Du uns helfen! Viel zu tun es gibt!
